<br>
it took me 31 days to make 50 on this charecter,i have little interest and the time to spend another 20 days levelling up my infiltrator on another server to get him to 50. i spent 80% of my time on my sb solo trying to level,basically due to lack of groups,i have no wish to repeat that painful process on another rogue class charecter.<br>
<br>
i also expect infils to get nerfed in the future,mabye as soon as the next patch. even if it doesnt happen,i started playing in beta, waited for release, spent 4 months waiting for them to make the class playable,came back 2 months ago,only to reach 50 and get nerfed back into what rogues were at the start of the game.<br>
<br>
realize im ranting a bit,but i guess in the end it comes down to being tired of paying for a product that hasnt really improved in quality since the release,and in many cases is more limiting then the first 2-3 months of the product were.<br>
