 <br>
 But now you come to a thread I started and state the same things. Sorry I have had enough! If you think other classes like infiltrator are more to your liking then go make one. If you don't want to level one up then go buy one or trade for one, but don't try and tell me that a class that I have played since November of last year is broken!<br>
 <br>
 No one at mythic said that shadowblades were supposed to be &quot;Shadowzerkers&quot;. No one said that they should be &quot;Critblades&quot;. That is all something PLAYERS came up with, trying to &quot;min/max&quot; the game. Will re-spec help this.. yes!<br>
 <br>
 Are shadowblades as good as Infiltrators? ..No. Are they better than at least 65% of the other classes in the game when it comes to RvR? ..YES!<br>
 <br>
 I am a Shadowblade.. level 50.. I been through the drill. You can try and tell me all you want to, but don't try to fill my head with notions of how weak shadowblades are, because I know different, ok?<br>
 <br>
 Sorry about the rant, but lets get back on topic.. If you want more for shadowblades then that is fine, but the two items I posted earlier in this thread are what we should be talking about.. A fix for Nightshades (they do need it) and A fix for server balancing in RvR so we can all find players to compete against.<br>
 <br>
 Take care!<br>
